## 6. Subagent Pattern (Isolated Tools)

The `subagent/` extension demonstrates spawning isolated `pi` processes for delegated tasks:

```typescript
// Spawn subagent with restricted tools and custom system prompt
const args = ["--mode", "json", "-p", "--no-session", "--tools", "read,grep,find,ls"];
// Subprocess receives a markdown agent definition with YAML frontmatter:
// ---
// name: scout
// description: Fast codebase reconnaissance
// tools: read, grep, find, ls, bash
// model: claude-haiku-4-5
// ---
```

Supports single, parallel (max 8, 4 concurrent), and chain modes with `{previous}` placeholder.

